{"tid":1444081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[變招] 根本好多醜聞核彈係手，依家欠既就係一場大型和理非遊行，去引爆佢地","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:36.000Z","uid":54684,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ac295a9a9b7d1daee5497e2d1138e476fdbc75","tid":1444081,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非合法遊行，係用來引爆醜聞核彈</strong><br />\n而我地已經儲左721恐怖襲擊，葉虎，女性畀人除褲除裙，打記者，推老伯，放生持棍黑幫....數之不盡，多到數唔到。<br />\n但我地<strong>仍然引爆唔到</strong>呢堆醜聞核彈，因為我地既精神放哂去密密麻麻既街頭衝擊<br />\n<br />\n無休止既街頭抗爭呢期有人不斷做，但全社會都睇到厭哂，效果已經開始減弱<br />\n我認為，係時候引爆醜聞核彈"},{"pid":"6130f6f6e1dbd9d999ff166d8c5d85561ecb3cb5","tid":1444081,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1172247830922821c087b20cd4463a8c7dc1d47c","tid":1444081,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n認同要有大型遊行宣揚一下中共港共惡行"},{"pid":"dfcb7589d47ce70329e91ff1672b6a6c6fc315c8","tid":1444081,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"要搵民陣"},{"pid":"a2f1afacc5bf81e22484592318a89484afa12e01","tid":1444081,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"881cefbb7c31eb82a0d526fdac0d90348e1f9869","tid":1444081,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW or NEVER</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tqhjh7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqhjh7N.jpg&h=2429b855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcMoKNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcMoKNN.png&h=cd877898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img s